\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bc28da76afcbf5383ee57b952ddd6b3b79a7ab","tid":1594250,"uid":274256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港島區<br />\n<br />\n1.小西灣/柴灣/筲箕灣沿海旁-鰂魚涌公園<br />\n<br />\n2.維園?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九龍區<br />\n<br />\n1.紅磡和黃公園<br />\n<br />\n2.?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新界區<br />\n<br />\n1. 沙田 城門河畔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 大埔 吐露港/白石角海濱長廊/科學園<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 馬鞍山海濱長廊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.荃灣公園二期, 海濱公園<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 青衣海濱公園<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6. 將軍澳海濱公園<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上資料來源均參照以下網頁<br />\n<br />\n(可細閱網頁內的地圖, 鄰近設施, 交通配套):<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fitz.hk/tag/香港跑步路線\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Ftag%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%B7%91%E6%AD%A5%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXToHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=9f226bcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fitz.hk/tag/香港跑步路線</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*歡迎大家比下意見, 因為本人唔太認熟悉禁多條路線, 唔知邊d路線安全, 希望有跑過嘅朋友比d意見/提議參考下*<br />\n<br />\n時間方面分兩節<br />\n第一節: 5-7pm 學生放學後<br />\n第二節: 8-10:30pm 學生放學連打工仔放工晚飯後<br />\n<br />\n可自由參與兩節或其中一節"},{"pid":"ebd049c75ae0ede8233f72df3d8c1940ec9e11b7","tid":1594250,"uid":274256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a7c99c3da812c21daa2b94c907daab425a3db99","tid":1594250,"uid":302944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"元朗國難民 想參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:10:43.000Z","msg":"巴打 知唔知元朗有咩跑步路線"},{"pid":"e4c496b2c868e0acc8bce80d6ca55f877451594f","tid":1594250,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}